<P>__{(into the phone)}
<D>__{no. it's fine. it's fine. don't send an ambulance. it's fine.}
<A>__{curtis clicks off the phone.}
<C>__{samantha}
<D>__{what are you doing?}
<A>__{curtis wraps his arms around her. he holds her tight. the sound of ambulance sirens approach from the distance. samantha speaks, her voice trembling.}
